#

Tofu Fried Rice

25 min
$8
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

SoyEgg (optional)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickHealthyComfort Food

Description

A quick and satisfying dish featuring crisp tofu and colorful veggies stir-fried with rice, perfect for a healthy meal!

Ingredients

  • cooked rice: 2 cups
  • firm tofu: 1 block (14 oz)
  • soy sauce: 3 tablespoons
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • mixed vegetables (carrots, peas, corn): 1 cup
  • green onions: 2, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • egg: 1 (optional)
